    "body": "Your code makes no mention of calldata. Please do not confuse the low-level EVM concept of call data and the more abstract notion of function call arguments. `uint256` is a [value type](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/v0.8.4/types.html#integers) and thus stored on the stack, which is modifiable.",
